ğŸ§  ML Model
Trained using Random Forest Classifier
Preprocessing: MinMaxScaler, StandardScaler
Accuracy: ~95%
Model and scalers are saved using Pickle (model.pkl, minmaxscaler.pkl, standscaler.pkl)
